{"tid":52558,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］M記今晚平安夜加價！連毒撚都恰！","createTime":"2016-12-24T07:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T13:25:08.000Z","uid":21707,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2f5296e76a95c6e6cc4c79f4da103bb4155370c","tid":52558,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6udyFj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6udyFj.jpg&h=948feb5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大型連鎖快餐店麥當勞繼今年初加價後，今日平安夜再度加價，平均加幅2.5%。13項加價產品中，以細薯條的加幅20%最高，有「窮人套餐」之稱的23元超值套餐則全部再加1元至24元，加幅4.3%。餐飲聯業協會表示，今年餐飲業經營環境不理想，成本持續上漲預計大型快餐店加價陸續有來。<br />\n<br />\n記者 蔡朗清<br />\n<br />\n麥當勞企業傳訊高級總監林婉梅表示，面對營運成本如薪金、食材等價格上漲，今日清晨4時起，13項食品會加價5毫及1元不等，超值早晨套餐、醒晨早餐、開心樂園餐、多款超值套餐的售價則維持不變，令整體平均加幅為2.5%，較綜合食品消費物價指數3.4%升幅為低，「今年第4季咖啡豆價格較去年同期上升咗25%」。<br />\n<br />\n麥當勞對上一次加價為今年1月，超值套餐、超值早晨套餐及醒晨早餐等3款套餐加價，平均加幅2.3%。今次則有13款產品加價，包括魚柳包、麥香雞、豬柳蛋漢堡、蘋果批、朱古力/士多啤梨新地及細薯條等6款超值選加價1元，當中細薯條加幅最高達兩成，由5元加至6元。<br />\n<br />\n「窮人套餐」3款23元超值套餐，年內第2次加價，同樣加1元售24元，加幅4.3%，包括脆辣雞腿包、雙層芝士孖堡及6件麥樂雞。另外，McCaf&eacute; 3款產品包括細杯裝意大利泡沫咖啡、榛子鮮奶咖啡，及中杯裝凍榛子鮮奶咖啡亦加價1元。新地筒加5毫，由3.5元至4元，加幅14.3%。<br />\n<br />\n林婉梅表示，麥當勞考慮加價時，已致力收窄受影響食品的範圍。明年1月1日首次一連兩天推出全日早餐，其中全新Bagel小麥圈早晨套餐全線減兩元發售。來年亦增設分店及招聘人手，目前正檢討薪酬調整事宜。問及麥當勞中港特許經營權花落誰家，她回應暫未有資料公佈。<br />\n<br />\n餐飲聯業協會會長黃家和表示，過去一年餐飲業經營環境不理想，中小型餐廳面對成本上漲也不敢加價，擔心客人流失，連鎖快餐店加價能力則較大，「麥當勞加價2.5%都算溫和」。他預料其他大型快餐店如大家樂、大快活等會陸續加價。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161224&amp;guid=56086242&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161224%26guid%3D56086242%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=2Qb4jeYzGtvxSAJgkmDsQxpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=ba4223ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161224%26guid%3D56086242%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=cdc32dea\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161224&amp;guid=56086242&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"02683a328ad9196ed9a45579c97cacf7aa3c3973","tid":52558,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/24W3Xo5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F24W3Xo5.jpg&h=c599f836&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c5dc4cbdc7ffc75afff6ab53d521efe3b34e24a","tid":52558,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/151551_86a049e8dfcdd3d52b9d74d7728233c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F151551_86a049e8dfcdd3d52b9d74d7728233c2.jpg&h=e34a68ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66e5bf495722102e846c836e501cb2129274feb0","tid":52558,"uid":17260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0b830b18310f72609308837e70eee353ffd97c","tid":52558,"uid":9930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:24:15.000Z","msg":"係咪想逼死我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4b58cfeb1b3ad640b6483372e2c442882053cb","tid":52558,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:30:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Rpg28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Rpg28.jpg&h=fae2b685&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48628829b3c8550e361e0afe8be36ec0e3fe2462","tid":52558,"uid":24335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T10:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/